rows.label: qst620303_msg0001
rows.name: I've got what you asked for.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0002
rows.name:
That's...
A Posystone...?

rows.label: qst620303_msg0003
rows.name: Wow! It's stunning...

rows.label: qst620303_msg0004
rows.name: And it'll suit Ondina to a tee.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0005
rows.name: I'm so happy I asked you guys...

rows.label: qst620303_msg0006
rows.name: Don't even mention it.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0007
rows.name:
So, what's next? The backdrop for
your proposal, was it?

rows.label: qst620303_msg0008
rows.name:
Yes!
That's right!

rows.label: qst620303_msg0009
rows.name:
...But lower your voice for Ether's sake!
We have to keep this a secret from
Ondina, don't we?

rows.label: qst620303_msg0010
rows.name: Ah, sorry!

rows.label: qst620303_msg0011
rows.name:
Well, moving on... I'm Liberalitan
myself, born and bred, so just let me
know what you're after.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0012
rows.name:
It'll have to be someplace romantic.
Talking about our love on a beach of
pure white sand... That kind of vibe.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0013
rows.name:
Hm. Baldotas Isle might work, then?
Not that I know much about the
"talking about our love" part...

rows.label: qst620303_msg0014
rows.name:
Well, may as well have a look at it!
Lead the way!

rows.label: qst620303_msg0015
rows.name: I got ya.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0016
rows.name:
Ondina dearest, a little something just
came up that I have to deal with.
Will you beokay by yourself for a bit?

rows.label: qst620303_msg0017
rows.name: Oh, did it now?

rows.label: qst620303_msg0018
rows.name: Well, all right, if it's just for a bit...

rows.label: qst620303_msg0019
rows.name:
I won't be long, promise. It's just,
I heard an old friend was in the area
so I thought I'd go say hello, is all.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0020
rows.name:
An old friend, is it? 
Well, be careful, now.

rows.label: qst620303_msg0021
rows.name: Will do!

rows.label: qst620303_msg0022
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Who does he think he's fooling,
anyway?
